						<summary>

						<p>Slab planted in a field called ‘Rāmayaseṭṭi-hola’.</p>						

						<p>Vīra-Ballāḷa III, 1337-38 A.D.</p>						

						<p>This badly damaged record is dated <hi rend="bold">Śaka [12]60, Īśvara, Phālguṇa, Thursday,</hi> the details being insufficient for verification. The Śaka year, which was current, corresponds to <hi rend="bold">1337-38 A.D.</hi> The record refers to Koṭīśvaradēva, probably a deity.</p>						

						</summary>
